query:
SELECT
                proofs.l1_batch_number
            FROM
                tee_proofs AS proofs
                JOIN tee_verifier_input_producer_jobs AS inputs
                ON proofs.l1_batch_number = inputs.l1_batch_number
            WHERE
                inputs.status = 'Successful'
                AND proofs.prover_taken_at IS NULL
            ORDER BY
                proofs.l1_batch_number ASC
            LIMIT
                1
